title: Requires the availability of and reimbursement for chiropractic care under the workers' compensation law to be provided on the same basis as care by a physician
summary: Requires the availability of and reimbursement for chiropractic care under the workers' compensation law to be provided on the same basis as care by a physician under such law.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the workers' compensation law, in relation to chiropractic care
